    "genset ~0.80 kgCO2e/kWh electrical (seed). REFINE PER PROJECT.",
    "",
    "OVERRIDE: add/replace rows in <project>/_BIM_COORD/sustainability/countries.json —",
    "a row with the same iso3 replaces the seed; new iso3 codes extend it. The latitude",
    "classifier (AshraeClimateZone) still applies for any city the user types that isn't",
    "listed. '*' is the flagged global default."
